content.problemStatement:
Observe the following C++ code that calculates a series sum:

```cpp
#include 
using namespace std;

int main() {
    int n = 5;
    int sum = 0;

    for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
        sum += i * i;
    }

    cout << "Sum = " << sum << endl;
    return 0;
}
```

